    • buildElementType

      @Nullable public ElementType buildElementType()
      This method is called whenever we need the ElementType instead of a real Element instance. This is currently used for ControlDefinition and Popup registering dynamically from Java using the Builder pattern.

      It is not used for the general Java builder call that generates real instances.

      Returns:
      the ElementType representation for this ElementBuilder
